
Project Outline
- Features
    - Add Folder(s)
    - Remove Folder(s)
    - Add new items to folder
    - Remove items within folder
    - List items within folder
    - Edit items within folder
    - Search for item in folder
    - Search for item using Title

- Properties 
    - Folder
        - ID
        - Title
        - Items[]
    - Item(s)
        - ID
        - Title

- FrontEnd
    - Blank screen
    - Edit Mode
    - Add button (auto saves)
    - Delete button

Issues
- main.py
    - support for adding multiple todo items
    - handle user input for valid ints
    - support for Deleting multiple todo items
    - support for Editing multiple todo items
    - folder tile change to dynamic - user imput